### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@token = <paste_access_token_here>
@clientId = <paste_client_id_here>
@projectId = <paste_project_id_here>

### 1) Crear proyecto
# @name createProject
POST {{baseUrl}}/project
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Reforma Oficinas Central",
  "projectCode": "PRJ-2024-001",
  "client": "{{clientId}}",
  "address": {
    "street": "Gran Vía",
    "number": "10",
    "postal": "28013",
    "city": "Madrid",
    "province": "Madrid"
  },
  "email": "obra@garcia.com",
  "notes": "Reforma integral de tres plantas"
}

### 2) Listar proyectos (con filtros)
GET {{baseUrl}}/project?page=1&limit=10&active=true&sort=-createdAt
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3) Filtrar proyectos por cliente
GET {{baseUrl}}/project?client={{clientId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4) Filtrar por nombre
GET {{baseUrl}}/project?name=Reforma
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5) Obtener proyecto concreto
GET {{baseUrl}}/project/{{projectId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6) Listar proyectos archivados
GET {{baseUrl}}/project/archived
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7) Actualizar proyecto
PUT {{baseUrl}}/project/{{projectId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Reforma Oficinas Central — Fase 2",
  "notes": "Añadida fase de pintura",
  "active": false
}

### 8) Archivar proyecto (soft delete)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/project/{{projectId}}?soft=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9) Borrar proyecto permanentemente (hard delete)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/project/{{projectId}}?soft=false
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10) Restaurar proyecto archivado
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/project/{{projectId}}/restore
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
